---
import MainLayout from "../../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Heal Program | Personal Training">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Heal (Rehab)</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">Rehabilitation programs to help you recover from injuries and improve mobility.</p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>Our Heal programs are designed to help you recover from injuries, address movement limitations, and build a foundation for pain-free living. Our expert trainers work closely with healthcare providers to ensure your rehabilitation program is safe, effective, and tailored to your specific needs.</p>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Program Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Comprehensive movement assessment</li>
        <li>Injury-specific rehabilitation protocols</li>
        <li>Progressive mobility training</li>
        <li>Pain management strategies</li>
        <li>Transition to functional strength training</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Common Areas of Focus</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4">
        <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">Lower Back Pain</div>
        <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">Shoulder Rehabilitation</div>
        <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">Knee Recovery</div>
        <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">Hip Mobility</div>
        <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">Postural Correction</div>
        <div class="card p-4 shadow-sm">Post-Surgery Rehabilitation</div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-dark transition">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
